        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Kuroda et al.</ENAMEX> (<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">2004</TIMEX>) further show that induction of anterior neural tissue initiated by
        Œ≤-catenin requires <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chordin</ENAMEX>, whereas formation of posterior neural tissue does not. This
